s/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果再加埋無掛p 再多一項 唔係就要重考咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:33:06.000Z","msg":"46嘅P牌3大規則:<br />\n1.掛p<br />\n2.時速最高70<br />\n3.有三條線嘅快速公路不可行快線<br />\n<br />\n以上只要犯是但一樣就加P半年<br />\n<br />\n另外只要觸犯扣分事項，都係加P半年<br />\n當然如果你比人告老危，個官有機會收番你個牌<br />\n<br />\n師兄你嘅問題:<br />\n70以下觸犯不扣分事項=罰錢<br />\n姐係扣風後超15或以下就無事<br />\n但扣風後超16或以上=扣3分加罰錢<br />\n<br />\n70以上超速，觸犯上面2. ，扣風後超1都係加半年<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講<br />\n你行50路扣風後超15<br />\n不用扣分事項，同違泊一樣交錢了事<br />\n<br />\n你行70路或70以上嘅路，就最多只可以行70<br />\n一旦任何正速比人影到，都可以加半年<br />\n<br />\n無掛p一定係加監，依家就係睇你當時係喺咩限速嘅路，同埋你超幾多"},{"pid":"b146ac1e00a5c49a9b0a35b7abf20798a10946d2","tid":2364143,"uid":145736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8f983be854d6143d54e1c8c9e21267f60243460","tid":2364143,"uid":23630,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a13bd00c741ed0e58e0aa998f4dd3854ead79ff0","tid":2364143,"uid":145736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41400ab88305744de18ebc352b027d1e3b9237b3","tid":2364143,"uid":23630,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T18:44:07.000Z","msg":"唔識咪撚誤導人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n70以下超15 (扣風後)只罰錢<br />\n70以上超就已經可以加P"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"70以下超15 唔係已經扣分=一項輕微錯誤=加監半年咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果再加埋無掛p 再多一項 唔係就要重考咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"